snippet.title: Big Boy Boxing - Official Animated Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Big Boy Boxing is a retro boxing boss rush action-adventure game developed by Soupmasters. Engage with fluid gameplay with slapstick comedy and a variety of different abilities from boxer to boxer. Big Boy Boxing is coming to PC at a later date with a demo available now on Steam.

#Gaming #Games #IGN
